@page "/about"

<section class="section">
    <H1>About</H1>
    <div class="prose" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
        <p>
            I'm @WebsiteKeys.Name — an integration architect and engineering manager based in
            Brisbane, Australia, who enjoys connecting complex systems and helping teams ship
            reliable software.
        </p>
        <p>
            Over my career I've worked across enterprise integration, cloud-native .NET on Azure,
            containers and Kubernetes, and increasingly the practical application of AI. I like
            building things that are simple to operate, well-observed, and pleasant for other
            engineers to work on.
        </p>
        <p>
            Outside of work I run a home lab, tinker with self-hosted infrastructure, and write
            about what I learn. This site is my space to share notes on .NET, cloud, DevOps and AI —
            all authored in Markdown and version-controlled.
        </p>

        <h2>A few things I focus on</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Designing integration and event-driven architectures that scale.</li>
            <li>Bringing cloud-native practices (IaC, CI/CD, observability) to teams.</li>
            <li>Leading and mentoring engineers.</li>
            <li>Exploring where AI genuinely helps developers.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
            Want to talk? Reach out on <a href="@WebsiteKeys.LinkedIn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
            or <a href="/contact">drop me a message</a>.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>
